# Build-time tooling (Spec Kit framework + Claude Code slash-command skills).
# These drive how this package was authored; they are NOT part of the
# RepoSkillOpt deliverable and must not be published. Kept locally so the
# spec-kit workflow still works, but untracked.
.claude/
.specify/
CLAUDE.md

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.vscode/
.idea/

# Working artifacts produced by the skill when run *inside this repo*.
# RepoSkillOpt's own .reposkillopt/ (if anyone exercises the skill here)
# is local context only and should not be committed. Sample reference
# outputs under examples/reference-output/.../.reposkillopt/ ARE part of
# the deliverable and MUST be tracked — the negation rule below preserves
# them.
.reposkillopt/
!examples/reference-output/*/.reposkillopt/
!examples/reference-output/*/.reposkillopt/**

# Local logs / scratch
*.log
.scratch/
